OL,3,GNorthern Ireland
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FDry with variable amounts of
OL,6,Fcloud and sunny spells through the
OL,7,Fday, best of the sunshine this
OL,8,Fafternoon. Northern counties may
OL,9,Fremain cloudy through the afternoon.
OL,10,FWarm in the southeast.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FThis evening will be dry,
OL,13,Fsome late brightness in the south.
OL,14,FThen the rest of the night will remain
OL,15,Fdry and becoming rather cloudy. Light
OL,16,Fwinds.
OL,17,
OL,18,CThursday:FAll parts will have a dry
OL,19,Fday. Rather cloudy in the morning but
OL,20,Fa few brighter spells in the afternoon.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
